Ungadulu is a shaman who is possessed by Nezikchened during the Legends' Quest. He has a combat level of 70, which becomes 169 when his demonic possession overcomes him. Despite this, Ungadulu cannot be attacked with melee or ranged weapons; he will throw players out of the Octagram, hitting them for between 4 and 10 damage. However, players can manually cast combat spells on him both inside and outside the Octagram to damage and kill him without being thrown by his spell.

After the quest, Yommi tree seeds and Holy force cannot be obtained.
